reviewText: I thought this would be funny cause "Jamie Foxx" headlines this ~ it is the worse MESS I have ever seen! NONE of the material is funny! Damn shame...

I've only seen the first installment of the laffapalooza series, but let me tell you...it was the worst stand-up I've ever seen.  Not ONE of those "comedians" were funny.  Don't let your being a fan of Jamie Foxx force you into buying this awful collection of irritating material.
